OL,3,CHow Alderney could harness excess
OL,4,Ctidal power to mine Bitcoin
OL,6,FAlderney could turn its excess
OL,7,Frenewable energy into digital money
OL,8,Fwith real value.
OL,10,FThe island is sending a delegation to
OL,11,Fthe Bitcoin Conference in Amsterdam as
OL,12,Fit seeks advice on how to turn excess
OL,13,Fpower from wind, tidal, and solar into
OL,14,Fthe cryptocurrency created by
OL,15,Fcomputers.
OL,17,FCompanies have already sought to
OL,18,Fharness the strong tides around
OL,19,FAlderney to produce cleaner energy for
OL,20,Fthe island.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/15
