OL,3,CHow Alderney could harness excess
OL,4,Ctidal power to mine Bitcoin
OL,6,FHowever, even the roaring power of the
OL,7,Fsea may not be enough to counteract
OL,8,Fthe huge energy costs associated with
OL,9,FBitcoin mining, and many still do not
OL,10,Fknow just where the digital currency -
OL,11,For cryptocurrency - comes from.
OL,13,FWhat is Bitcoin?
OL,15,FBitcoin is a digital currency that
OL,16,Fexists purely online.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/15
