OL,3,CHow Alderney could harness excess
OL,4,Ctidal power to mine Bitcoin
OL,6,FA network of powerful computers - or
OL,7,Fcrypto miners - work to solve puzzles
OL,8,Fdigitally, with winners being rewarded
OL,9,Fwith newly created Bitcoins.
OL,11,FCrypto expert James Butterfill
OL,12,Fexplained that mining is a way to
OL,13,Fencourage people to use the network,
OL,14,Fwhich in turn secures the currency
OL,15,Feven more.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/15
