OL,3,CHow Alderney could harness excess
OL,4,Ctidal power to mine Bitcoin
OL,6,F"I think if you walked into a server
OL,7,Froom and a Bitcoin mining centre, you
OL,8,Fprobably couldn't tell the
OL,9,Fdifference," James said. "They're just
OL,10,Fcomputers on racks and they do one
OL,11,Fthing: mine Bitcoin.
OL,13,F"Ultimately, it is a computer
OL,14,Fconsuming energy, and it's that
OL,15,Fconsumption of energy that gives
OL,16,FBitcoin value.
OL,18,F"The computers solve a mathematical
OL,19,Fpuzzle, and the miners get rewarded
OL,20,Fwith Bitcoin for doing so, and it's
OL,21,Feconomically lucrative to do so.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/15
