OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F384A1762966898
OL,3,CHow Alderney could harness excess
OL,4,Ctidal power to mine Bitcoin
OL,6,F"It creates a global, decentralised
OL,7,Fnetwork that secures Bitcoin. It's
OL,8,Fsomething that everyone can use, so
OL,9,Fthe more miners involved, the more
OL,10,Fsecure Bitcoin becomes."
OL,12,FWhy Alderney?
OL,14,FWhile countries like China have banned
OL,15,Fbanks from trading in cryptocurrency,
OL,16,FAlderney hopes to capitalise on the
OL,17,FBitcoin boom.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/15
