OL,3,CHow Alderney could harness excess
OL,4,Ctidal power to mine Bitcoin
OL,6,FIt's not the first time the island has
OL,7,Ftaken an interest in Bitcoin. In 2013,
OL,8,Fthey announced a plan to mint Bitcoins
OL,9,Finto physical gold-plated coins.
OL,11,FNow, as the island explores its
OL,12,Frenewable resources, there is an
OL,13,Fopportunity to use the "stranded
OL,14,Fenergy" - or the power made in excess
OL,15,Fwhen harvesting any energy source - to
OL,16,Frun Bitcoin-mining computers.
OL,18,F"I think it's very easy to baulk at
OL,19,Fthis idea and think it's preposterous,
OL,20,Fbut it could help with energy
OL,21,Fsecurity," James added.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
