OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F384A1762966898
OL,3,CHow Alderney could harness excess
OL,4,Ctidal power to mine Bitcoin
OL,6,F"Renewable energies are very expensive
OL,7,Fto create, and if you mine Bitcoin
OL,8,Fwith the excess energy, then the
OL,9,Fpayback period is a lot shorter for
OL,10,Frenewable investments.
OL,12,F"I think in the long term, it's quite
OL,13,Fa prudent move."
OL,15,FRepresentative Edward Hill, Chair of
OL,16,FPolicy and Finance for the States of
OL,17,FAlderney, thinks that the island needs
OL,18,Fto capitalise on using its "very big
OL,19,Ftidal flow".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/15
