OL,3,CHow Alderney could harness excess
OL,4,Ctidal power to mine Bitcoin
OL,6,F"There will be no risk, because all
OL,7,Fwe're talking about is people coming
OL,8,Fto this island and making it their
OL,9,Ffiscal base, paying tax, and bringing
OL,10,Fyounger people to the island.
OL,12,F"We've got tidal, wind, and solar, but
OL,13,Fthat has to be sold somewhere. With
OL,14,Fthe potential wind farm, we're
OL,15,Fprobably going to do contracts with
OL,16,Fthe United Kingdom and France.
OL,17,FHowever, it is also useful to have a
OL,18,Fmarket that will buy the surplus
OL,19,Fenergy from these providers, which is
OL,20,Fbased in island and not subject to
OL,21,Fpolitical risk.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/15
