OL,3,CHow Alderney could harness excess
OL,4,Ctidal power to mine Bitcoin
OL,6,FHowever, some Alderney politicians,
OL,7,Fsuch as Representative Alex Snowdon,
OL,8,Fhave said they are a "little cautious"
OL,9,Fabout how they approach investing in
OL,10,FBitcoin mining infrastructure.
OL,12,F"I look forward to getting feedback
OL,13,Ffrom my colleagues who are involved in
OL,14,FBitcoin about what these opportunities
OL,15,Fmay or may not be," he explained. "I
OL,16,Fbelieve we should be cautious with
OL,17,FBitcoin because while it's an
OL,18,Finteresting market, it's uncertain.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/15
