OL,3,CHow Alderney could harness excess
OL,4,Ctidal power to mine Bitcoin
OL,6,FAdditionally, while Bitcoin's value
OL,7,Fhas remained relatively secure, there
OL,8,Fis a finite amount, prompting
OL,9,Fquestions as to whether Alderney can
OL,10,Fbe ready to mine crypto before it runs
OL,11,Fout.
OL,13,FAn onshore wind farm has been put
OL,14,Fforward for Fort Albert, and a solar
OL,15,Ffarm is being considered for La
OL,16,FCorvee, east of the airport, but no
OL,17,Fconstruction has begun.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/15
