OL,3,CHow Alderney could harness excess
OL,4,Ctidal power to mine Bitcoin
OL,6,FThe company Spiralis was also meant to
OL,7,Ftest its tidal energy generators in
OL,8,FAlderney, but shifted its plans to
OL,9,FOrkney, with hopes of rolling out its
OL,10,Fhydro-power spirals in two years' time.
OL,12,F"It's all very good to have visions
OL,13,Fand ideas, but in my view, the
OL,14,Ftimeline for the potential would be
OL,15,Fquite a long time away, and Bitcoin
OL,16,Fmining takes a tremendous amount of
OL,17,Fpower to deliver and to be able to be
OL,18,Fimplemented," explained Representative
OL,19,FSnowdon.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/15
