OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F384A1762966898
OL,3,CHow Alderney could harness excess
OL,4,Ctidal power to mine Bitcoin
OL,6,F"I'm not quite sure that this vision
OL,7,Fis actually deliverable on a little
OL,8,Fisland, and whether that would
OL,9,Factually work. Maybe in ten to fifteen
OL,10,Fyears, but will Bitcoin be around in
OL,11,Ften to fifteen years? That's the
OL,12,Fquestion I can't answer."
